snippet.title: Food Truck Empire - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the ultimate food truck tycoon in this upcoming game, Food Truck Empire, where you will customize food trucks, create your menus, and find hungry customers across multiple cities in the United States. Check out the announcement trailer for a look at what to expect with this 3D tycoon game that's headed to PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #FoodTruckEmpire
